<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbe8d3836-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s8272"><num value="8272">§ 8272.</num><heading> Photovoltaic energy program</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is hereby established a photovoltaic energy commercialization program for the accelerated procurement and installation of photovoltaic solar electric systems for electric production in Federal facilities.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbe8d3837-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/95/619/tV/s563">Pub. L. 95–619, title V, § 563</ref>, <date date="1978-11-09">Nov. 9, 1978</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/92/3280">92 Stat. 3280</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
